     H            Y.
      ** AB#R2L4 ************************************************************
      *  ..HONDA LABEL ---- CHECK FOR SERVICE PART LOCATION                 *
      *  LEC  10/16/19                                                      *
      ***********************************************************************
      *
     FAB#WP2U IF  E           K        DISK
      *
      ***********************************************************
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           SPFLG   1
      *
      *  read through container label workfile and check for any
      *      location not a final location. if not 01-99 then set
      *      service part flag on and exit.
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    SPFLG
      *
     C                     READ AB#WP2U                  52
      *
     C           *IN52     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           U2LOC2    IFGE '01'
     C           U2LOC2    ANDLE'99'
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       SPFLG
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ AB#WP2U                  52
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      ***********************************************************
